neralized linear models, such\nas logistic regression and $p$-probit regression. Our upper bounds are\nparameterized by a complexity parameter $\\mu$ introduced by [MSSW2018], and we\nshow the first lower bounds showing that a linear dependence on $\\mu$ is\nnecessary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Jul 2022 19:40:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 15:40:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 17 Dec 2022 17:22:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-20"}
