fy good\ncommuting vector fields for the advection-diffusion operator on the sphere. Our\nresults in this direction may be useful to other models in collective dynamics,\nwhere an orientation variable is involved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2022 08:29:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2022 08:29:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-19"}
