ind detection.\nFinally, using the Nicer spectra alone, we followed the system while it was\nfading to quiescence. During the outburst decay, as the spectral shape\nhardened, the hot spot on the neutron star surface cooled down and shrank, a\ntrend which could be consistent with the pure power-law spectrum observed\nduring quiescence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2022 14:31:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-03"}
