ains EEG and EMG signals that were recorded\nsimultaneously, we manage to conclude the feasibility and effectiveness of the\nnovel system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2022 14:51:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 03:41:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 12:31:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-10"}
